  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2020-04-10T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Coronavirus Help And Response Initiative Through Year 2022 Act or the CHARITY 2022 Act\n\nThis bill allows a taxpayer a deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for charitable contributions for a taxable year beginning in 2020-2022, even if such taxpayer does not otherwise itemize deductions. The deduction may not exceed one-third of the taxpayer's standard deduction amount."
  }, 
